[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    21[0m:[38;5;10m[49m That said, three correctness-and-compliance gaps at HIGH severity need attention before publication, plus the chapter-pattern set of MEDIUM and LOW items. The recipe contains explicit `<!-- TODO (TechWriter): Expert review SX/AX/NX -->` markers (S1 through S6, A1 through A8, N1 through N2) that anticipate the expert-review findings; the editor's job is to reconcile these against the actual findings and consolidate them in the next pass.
