[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    27[0m:[38;5;10m[49m (3) **Per-cohort engagement-and-attrition-and-crisis-screening-sensitivity-and-warm-handoff-completion-and-companion-pattern-violation-and-citation-coverage-and-equity-disparity monitoring with launch-gate discipline architecturally implicit despite recipe's own elevation as central trap, with recipe-distinct crisis-screening-false-negative-rate-as-life-safety-acute-launch-gate-metric and companion-pattern-violation-rate-as-launch-gate and warm-handoff-completion-rate-as-launch-gate and per-language-and-per-cultural-context-and-per-condition-and-per-age-cohort-and-per-channel-equity-monitoring extensions.** Same chapter pattern as 11.1-11.7 Finding A1 with recipe-distinct life-safety-acute extensions. The recipe correctly elevates per-cohort monitoring in five separate places (Cross-Cutting Design Points, Production-Gaps, Honest Take's twelfth trap, Where-it-Struggles, Where-the-Field-Has-Moved equity discussion). Despite this thorough prose elevation, the architecture pattern, the diagram, and the pseudocode do not specify per-cohort launch-gate threshold values, two-axis and three-axis cohort stratification, per-cohort crisis-screening false-negative rate as recipe-distinct life-safety-acute launch-gate metric ("less than 2% as launch-gate, ideally under 1% for high-risk dimensions"), per-cohort companion-pattern-violation rate as recipe-distinct ethics-acute launch-gate metric, per-cohort warm-handoff-completion rate as recipe-distinct safety-acute launch-gate metric, per-cohort engagement-attrition rate at 30/90/180-day windows as recipe-distinct central-operational-risk metric, per-cohort PHQ-9 trajectory accuracy and GAD-7 trajectory accuracy and C-SSRS trajectory accuracy and hospitalization-rate trajectory across multi-window correlation as recipe-distinct quality-acute metrics, per-cohort therapeutic-content-citation-coverage rate, per-cohort regulatory-disclaimer-presence rate (recurring "I'm a tool, not a therapist" framing presence), per-cohort safety-plan-integration completeness rate, per-cohort sensitive-disclosure handling completeness rate, per-cohort mandatory-reporting routing appropriateness rate, per-cohort scope-violation rate (therapy-attempted, diagnosis-attempted, medication-recommendation-attempted, trauma-processing-attempted, harm-content), per-cohort equity-disparity flags by sex, race, age, language, condition, age cohort, and social-determinant flag with statistical-significance flags. Recipe-acute and life-safety-acute amplification because the bot is the chapter's first life-safety-acute recipe and the operational-and-clinical-and-regulatory-and-ethical exposures the recipe sells (avoided suicide attempts, avoided psychiatric hospitalizations, sustained-engagement-with-evidence-based-therapeutic-content, regulatory-defensibility) are bounded above by all of the per-cohort metrics simultaneously. The recipe contains explicit `<!-- TODO (TechWriter): Expert review A1 (HIGH) -->` and `<!-- TODO (TechWriter): Expert review S2 (HIGH) -->` markers anticipating this finding.
