[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    31[0m:[38;5;10m[49m Voice is excellent. **Em dash count: 0** (verified via grep for the `—` character against the published draft). The 70/30 vendor balance is maintained: AWS service names appear first in the AWS Implementation section. CC voice is consistent throughout: the Sam-at-11:47-PM-on-a-Wednesday opening grounds the engineer-explaining-something-cool register exactly with appropriate gravity for the life-safety domain. Self-deprecating expertise lands well throughout the Honest Take. Healthcare-domain accuracy is broadly consistent (HIPAA references correct; 42 CFR Part 2 reference correct for substance-use-treatment records; FHIR CarePlan, Goal, Observation, Communication resource references correct; 988 Suicide and Crisis Lifeline reference correct including the 2022 launch date and the call-text-chat modalities; SAMHSA National Helpline reference correct; C-SSRS reference correct including the public-domain framing; PHQ-9 reference correct including the item-9-suicidal-ideation framing; GAD-7 reference correct; AUDIT reference correct; Stanley-Brown Safety Planning Intervention reference correct; American Psychiatric Association and American Psychological Association practice-guideline references correct; FDA SaMD framework reference correct; FDA Clinical Decision Support Software Final Guidance (2022) reference correct; FDA-authorized prescription digital therapeutics framing correct including reSET-O for opioid use disorder, Somryst for chronic insomnia; the AI-companion-product-category framing operationally accurate including the documented-incidents-of-harm framing; CBT, behavioral activation, DBT skills, ACT, motivational interviewing modality references correct; Edinburgh Postnatal Depression Scale reference correct; the Lyra/Spring Health/Talkspace/BetterHelp/Headspace Health/Wysa/Woebot product-and-evidence-base framing operationally accurate). Architectural accuracy is high. The ten-stage decomposition is the archite